title: Destroy All Humans 2 Reprobed
description: Crypto is back with a license to probe. The alien invader returns, groovier than ever. Experience the swinging ‘60s in all its chemical-induced glory and take revenge on the KGB for blowing up your mothership. You’ll have to form alliances with members of the very species you came to enslave. Carnivores: Dinosaur Hunt

system_requirements.Processor: AMD / Intel CPU running at 3.0 GHz

game_info.Version: v1.0.362 | Full  Skin Pack + Official Orchestral Score + Shared/Split Screen Co-op
